imdb.plot outline: Curious kids find themselves trapped in a bizarre subterranean world controlled by the megalomaniacal 'Machine' and her minion 'The Inquisitor' in this fast-paced, gooey, irreverent game. To win their freedom, two teams of two 'Inquisitive' go head-to-head as their problem-solving abilities and scientific knowledge are put to the test. The winning teams are deemed Steam Punks. and transported back home.
imdb.title: Steam Punks!
